_:N8f497e519a224e19a63e0948d0c315ed <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Josh MacAlister was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State State (Minister for Children and Families) at the Department for Education on 7 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was elected as the MP for Whitehaven and Workington in July 2024.</p>\n" .
